# Git Conventions

## Commits
`<type>(<scope>): <description>` — keep under 72 chars.

Types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, style, test, chore, perf
Scope (optional): classification, tariff, ui, auth, compliance

## Branches
- `feature/<description>` / `fix/<description>` / `refactor/<area>`
- main → production
